quran[21{c,v,t}:
26,40,"shayad ke humjadogaron ke deen hi par reh jayen agar woh ghalib rahay """
26,41,"jab jadugar maidan mein aa gay to unhon ne firaon se kaha"" hamein inaam to miley ga agar hum ghalib rahay? """
26,42,"is ne kaha"" haan, aur tum to is waqtmuqarabain mein shaamil ho jao ge """
26,43,"moose ne kaha"" phenko jo tumhe phenkna hai """
26,44,"unhon ne foran apni rasiyaan aur lathyan pheink den aur bolay"" firaon ke Iqbal se hum hi ghalib rahen ge """
26,45,phir moose ne apna asa phenka to yakayak woh un ke jhutay karishmo ko harap karta chala ja raha tha
26,46,is par saaray jadugar be ikhtiyar sjday mein gir parre
26,47,"aur bol utthay ke"" maan gay hum rab alameen ko"
26,48,"moose aur haroon ke rab ko """
26,49,"firaon ne kaha"" tum moose ki baat maan gay qabal is ke ke mein tumhe ijazat deta! zaroor yeh tumhara bara hai jis ne tumhe jaadoo sikhaya hai acha, abhi tumhe maloom howa jata hai, mein tumahray haath paon mukhalif simtao mein کٹواﺅں ga aur tum sab ko suli charha dun ga """
26,50,"unhon ne jawab diya"" kuch parwah nahi, hum apne rab ke huzoor poanch jayen ge"
26,51,"aur hamein tawaqqa hai ke hamara rab hamaray gunah maaf kar day ga kyunkay sab se pehlay hum imaan laaye hain """
26,52,"hum ne moose ko wahi bhaije ke"" raton raat mere bundon ko le kar nikal jao, tumhara peecha kya jaye ga """
26,53,is par firaon ne ( faujein jama karne ke liye ) shehron mein naqeeb bhaij diye
26,54,"( aur kehla bheja ) ke"" yeh kuch muthi bhar log hain"
26,55,aur unhon ne hum ko bohat naraaz kya hai
26,56,"aur hum aik aisi jamaat hain jis ka Shewa har waqt chokanna rehna hai """
26,57,iss terhan hum inhen un ke baghoon aur chashmon
26,58,aur khazanon aur un ki behtareen qiyam gaahon se nikaal laaye
26,59,"yeh to howa unn ke sath, aur ( doosri taraf ) bani Israel ko hum ne un sab cheezon ka waris kar diya"
26,60,subah hotay hi yeh log unn ke taqub mein chal parre
